reviews.review_text: Hamburg Show was a good one with songs first played on this tour and only played on this tour. Same size place as Essen but much better playing than Essen imo. I saw 5 shows in Germany on this tour and Hamburg was the 2nd or 3rd best after the 2 Berlin shows. The first Berlin show being the best. But this one is a keeper.
